HEADWORD: Sulphato-
<hw>Sul"pha*to-</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A combining
form (also used adjectively) denoting a <xex>sulphate as an
ingredient</xex> in certain double salts; <as>as,
<ex>sulphato</ex>-carbonate</as>.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
